data.description:
Great opportunity to live as as far away possible from the Greater El Paso Area but yet within stone´s throw to all the major benefits a vibrant can give you within a 15 mintues drive. You get to keep all the upside of solitude, peace and quiet so you can go about your life at your own pace.

This propety consists of two parcels that total 14.14 Acres. The smaller parcel contains two mobile homes, several utility sheds, garages and other infrastructure that can allow someone to have his/her own business running from the comfort of home.

The extra acreage can be held on for the long term so you can capitalize on the future growth of El Paso Greater Metro Area. You can always find something to do with 11 Acres of Land. Talk to us or your agent, I am sure we can give you some good ideas.

The smaller parcel (The Living one) property has a water well, two septic systems, prepared with Propane Gas intakes and connected to Electricity. Call us for more details.
